  "text": "25HC (Sigma-Aldrich) was dissolved in DMSO and treatments were carried out at varying concentrations (final DMSO concentration 0.01%). Oleic acid (Calbiochem, San Diego, CA, USA) was prepared as per [CITATION_1] and used at a final concentration of 400 μM in the form of fatty acid-supplemented medium for 4 h. Acetylated-LDL (acLDL) experiments were conducted using fluorescently-conjugated Alexa Fluor 1 594 acLDL acquired from Molecular Probes.",
